room_title: Escape room "Sherlock Adventure!" by Escape Room BCS in College Station
room_address: 907 Harvey Rd Ste B College Station, TX 77840
room_description: Your appointment with Sherlock Holmes, the world’s first consulting detective, goes terribly awry when his nemesis Professor Moriarty decides that this is the day to seek revenge. As soon as you enter the detective’s sitting room, the door locks with a sickening crack. You have only an hour to locate Queen Victoria’s most valuable diamond, which Holmes has cleverly hidden somewhere in 221B Baker Street. Explore Sherlock’s flat to find the priceless Koh-i-noor diamond. Don’t get too comfortable: more than your own fate may be at stake!
